    <item>
      <title>Grifols 通过特殊债券条款向 Brookfield 敞开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/grifols-keeps-door-open-to-brookfield-with-special-bond-clause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Grifols SA 在其 13 亿欧元（14 亿美元）的私人债务配售中加入了一项条款，允许 Brookfield Asset Management Ltd. 提前为该交易进行再融资 — — 这表明这家西班牙制药商为这家私募股权公司采取另一种方式敞开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/grifols-keeps-door-open-to-brookfield-with-special-bond-clause</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:33:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰钢铁制造商暂停顿涅茨克煤矿运营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/ukrainian-steelmaker-halts-operation-at-coal-mine-in-donetsk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰最大的钢铁制造商 Metinvest BV 已暂停其位于顿涅茨克地区波克罗夫斯克附近的煤炭生产基地的运营，因为该镇成为近几个月来与俄罗斯军队最激烈的战斗的中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/ukrainian-steelmaker-halts-operation-at-coal-mine-in-donetsk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势缓解供应过剩担忧，油价缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价扭转早前的跌势，交易至每桶 70 美元上方，因为中东局势升级的可能性让多头有信心买入，尽管前景日益悲观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 23:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
